d his technical skills are highly relevant. The interpersonal issues are limited to tone and perception, which are less likely to jeopardize crew safety than the more severe communication or temperament problems seen in the other candidates.\n**Therefore, I vote for Candidate\u202fB.**\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
